Document: EditorFeatureProfile
Path: godot/classes/class_editorfeatureprofile.rst
Summary: Defines a set of features that can be enabled or disabled for specific editor profiles.

EditorFeatureProfile

Inherits: Resource < Object

A profile that defines a set of features that can be enabled or disabled for specific editor profiles. This is used to customize the editor's behavior and appearance based on the project's needs or the user's preferences. For example, you can disable certain features to simplify the interface or improve performance.
